title: Find Value By Investing In Diversity
text: Add diversity to your investment questions along with valuations.

title: 'Concerned' scientists funded by Chan Zuckerberg Initiative urge Facebook to tamp down on incendiary speech
text: Scientists backed by the Chan Zuckerberg Initiative urge Facebook to take a stronger stand on misinformation and incendiary speech.

title: Scientists Funded By Chan Zuckerberg Initiative Accuse Facebook Of Ignoring Its Own Policies On Trump Post
text: More than 140 scientists urged Facebook to tighten its policy on misinformation, and accused Trump of making “incendiary statements.”
